OL,3,CTeignmouth Community Hub faces closure
OL,4,Cwithout urgent funding
OL,6,FA vital community hub in Teignmouth
OL,7,Fthat has supported vulnerable and
OL,8,Felderly residents since the late 1970s
OL,9,Fis at risk of closure unless
OL,10,Fsignificant funding can be secured.
OL,12,FThe Alice Cross Centre provides a wide
OL,13,Frange of activities and support
OL,14,Fservices, including a memory cafe for
OL,15,Fthose with dementia and their carers,
OL,16,Flunch clubs, grief support, line
OL,17,Fdancing, yoga, and youth drama groups.
