OL,3,CTeignmouth Community Hub faces closure
OL,4,Cwithout urgent funding
OL,6,FManagers say the centre, which many
OL,7,Frely on as a lifeline, is now in a
OL,8,Fcritical financial position due to
OL,9,Frising costs and a reduction in
OL,10,Favailable grant funding.
OL,12,FJenny Jenkins, a regular at the
OL,13,Fcentre, explained its importance: "We
OL,14,Fwould be very lonely and isolated
OL,15,Fbecause I am a full-time carer as
OL,16,Fwell, so I am having to do things that
OL,17,FI hate, and coming here, I can forget
OL,18,Fall my worries. That really is what
OL,19,FAlice Cross has done for me."
OL,26,@uD@cOU{D@]O]
