OL,3,CTeignmouth Community Hub faces closure
OL,4,Cwithout urgent funding
OL,6,FPamela Martin, another visitor, shared
OL,7,Fa similar sentiment: "It's my life now
OL,8,Fbecause I can't leave my husband's
OL,9,Fside. He can't be left alone for a
OL,10,Fminute. It's a great help. It's
OL,11,Fsomething we look forward to all the
OL,12,Ftime, and we have friends here, you
OL,13,Fknow. It's always happy like this.
OL,14,FThis has not just been put on for you.
OL,15,FIt's always like this, it's happy, you
OL,16,Fknow, it's lovely."
OL,18,FThe centre was established in 1978 and
OL,19,Fhas become a cornerstone of the
OL,20,Fcommunity, particularly for
OL,21,FTeignmouth's aging population.
