OL,3,CTeignmouth Community Hub faces closure
OL,4,Cwithout urgent funding
OL,6,FHowever, the financial situation is
OL,7,Fdire. Andy Langford, Chair of
OL,8,FTrustees, explained: "Day-to-day
OL,9,Frunning costs are going up and up all
OL,10,Fthe time. Fuel bills, food bills,
OL,11,Fsalaries, etc., they have to be found.
OL,13,F"The last two years have seen us
OL,14,Foperate at a loss of over thirty
OL,15,Fthousand pounds. We are reliant upon
OL,16,Fquite a lot of grant funding. As we
OL,17,Fknow, everybody's after grant funding
OL,18,Fand grants are now being shared more
OL,19,Fand more widely with less and less
OL,20,Famounts."
