OL,3,CTeignmouth Community Hub faces closure
OL,4,Cwithout urgent funding
OL,6,FThe centre currently requires an
OL,7,Fadditional #5,000 to #8,000 each month
OL,8,Fto cover costs. Without this, they
OL,9,Frisk having to cut staff and reduce
OL,10,Fservices. At the current rate, funds
OL,11,Fmay run out by mid-2025.
OL,13,FTo combat the crisis, the centre has
OL,14,Flaunched a campaign called "Give a
OL,15,FLittle, Help a Lot," urging locals to
OL,16,Fmake regular donations. These funds
OL,17,Fare critical to maintaining programs
OL,18,Fsuch as the meals prepared and
OL,19,Fdelivered to residents' homes.
