OL,6,FVolunteer Janet Oettl highlighted the
OL,7,Fvalue of this service: "I can only
OL,8,Fspeak from the cooking side, but I
OL,9,Fthink food does connect people,
OL,10,Fdoesn't it? And we send out a lot of
OL,11,Ffood to other people who are then
OL,12,Freally happy to get it, you know, warm
OL,13,Ffood, and they also feel connected to
OL,14,Fus then."
